I absolutely love that this service is available. You know how much of a pain it is to get yourself out of the house and to the doctor's office or urgent care center when you feel like garbage... The entire process was simple, quick and even while feeling so sick, it was not a hassle, whatsoever. The only complaint I have is there was an echo of my voice throughout the entire session and the physician's assistant seemed to have some trouble understanding or hearing me at certain points during the session but it was nothing so bad as to cause me to not use this service again. I would ABSOLUTELY recommend this service to anyone that is looking for quick, efficient and complete medical care!
